Mario Balotelli has been charged by the Football Association for posting an allegedly abusive or insulting image on social media.

It is unlikely, though, this incident will result in the end of the striker’s Liverpool career, as the club have no plans to sell him in the January transfer window.

Balotelli’s contract has clauses in it relating to his behaviour but Liverpool are continuing to work with the 24-year-old.

